The '''''Enforcer''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|Nebulon-B frigate]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The ship was sent to protect an Imperial commercial staging area near [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan]] but arrived too late to prevent the [[Raid above Bonadan|destruction]] of valuable supply containers and freighters by two [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]]. Later after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], it arrived along with the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] ''[[Blacken]]'' after [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]] along with an [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] [[Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport|Stormtrooper Transport]] [[Raider (Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport)|''Raider'']] stole Imperial food supplies.

